com.ikalagaming.plugins.PluginManager

  • Packages that use PluginManager 
    Package Description
    com.ikalagaming.gui
    Common graphical user interfaces that work with the engine.
    com.ikalagaming.plugins
    Manages plugins, which are distinct subsystems of the engine that can be dynamically swapped in and out or enabled/disabled during runtime.
    com.ikalagaming.system
    Provides ways of communicating with and controlling the core of the engine (event manager, plugin manager) using events.
